Question: The weights in the right image are in use by a man, unlike the weights in the left image.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://images.pond5.com/guys-taking-and-putting-back-footage-081542372_prevstill.jpeg

Right image URL: https://i.ytimg.com/vi/WEMFJ1y37Bc/maxresdefault.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the weights in use by a man?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the weights in use by a man?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='not {ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
